{"tid":158850,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[撤旦/潛意識] 歐美流行音樂內含魔鬼訊息???","createTime":"2017-03-16T14:32:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T06:25:52.000Z","uid":47276,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"41d681b26cd1b59699b1c256823483d7bf2578f5","tid":158850,"uid":47276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:32:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r91yS8BWecA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dr91yS8BWecA&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=8baa7af1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r91yS8BWecA</a><br />\n光明會在流行曲入面滲透撤旦訊息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最近看到關於撤旦利用音樂傳播思想的文章<br />\n覺得好有趣 <br />\n關於隱藏訊息可以影響人的潛意識同驅使人有做某些事的傾向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其中指話 <br />\n<br />\nSubliminal 一種可以跨過人意識（Consciousness）之防衛網，去破壞人類的下意識（Subconscious）及潛意識（Unconscious）領域的一種技術。其方法是用嘈吵的音樂聲、叫聲、歌聲，去覆蓋著另一把聲音所唱的另一些歌詞。<br />\n<br />\n例子:<br />\n在1956年，美國有一間叫Subliminal Project Company，嘗試在戲院放映中的電影裏，每15秒就加一格菲林「可樂」的圖像，但在人的視覺中，是無法看到一閃而過的可樂鏡頭，但當散場後，竟發覺不少觀眾有想去飲「可樂」的慾望。<br />\n<br />\n在1978年，美國亦有一個實驗報告發表，於37間超級市場裏，在播放中的輕音樂裏面同時有一把肉耳聽不到的微聲在說：「你很誠實，不會偷東西，不會犯法&hellip;&hellip;」結果，在九個月後，超級市場高賣的損失減少了四百多萬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無人有研究過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n參考文章:<br />\n<a href=\"https://binbin.wordpress.com/2008/01/01/%E6%92%92%E6%97%A6%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbinbin.wordpress.com%2F2008%2F01%2F01%2F%25E6%2592%2592%25E6%2597%25A6%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2585%25B7%2F&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=1b038ae5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://binbin.wordpress.com/2008/01/01/%E6%92%92%E6%97%A6%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/</a>"},{"pid":"fc30bf6672adac8b80a959f00f060dc647d63008","tid":158850,"uid":47276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:35:05.000Z","msg":"打錯<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撒</span></strong>"},{"pid":"97ae252a93883f0666ccf49d4508148af9dd3a27","tid":158850,"uid":47276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c36e634f57524d6e14ccbe9a810b153189bce5","tid":158850,"uid":47276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T15:01:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a65b0c5b7296ad5b72a08da93a065f6e23ab50","tid":158850,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T15:08:24.000Z","msg":"成日針對nigga呢個詞語<img src=\"/assets